The '''M-40 light repeating blaster''', also known as the '''"Thunderbolt"''', was a [[Repeating blaster/Legends|repeating blaster]] produced by [[Merr-Sonn Munitions, Inc./Legends|Merr-Sonn]]. It was mounted on a [[bipod]] and produced powerful red bolts. They were impractical as close-quarter weapons however.

[[Liane Trevval|Chalk]] notably wielded a Thunderbolt as her favorite weapon. They were also carried by the four hooded men sent to kill [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]] on [[Vohai]].

In [[137 ABY]], a version of the Thunderbolt dubbed Mark 7 was produced and were desired by [[Pirate/Legends|pirates]].<ref name="SWLegacy37">[[Legacy (2006) 37|''Legacy'' (2006) 37]]</ref>

